DOC.brief_summary: This is a phase I, open label, healthy volunteers, ADME study with single oral administration of [14C] AZD5069.
DOC.brief_title: Open Label, Healthy Volunteers, ADME Study With Single Oral Administration of [14C] AZD5069
DOC.criteria: Have a body mass index (BMI) of ≥18 and ≤30 kg/m2 and weight of ≥50 kg and ≤100 kg. Regular daily bowel movements (ie, production of at least 1 stool per day). Nonsmoker or exsmoker who has not used tobacco or nicotine products for ≥6 months prior to Visit 1 Healthy Male volunteers aged 50 and over Healthy volunteers who have been exposed to radiation levels above background (eg, through Xray examination) of >5 mSv in the last year, >10 mSv in the last 5 years, or a cumulative total of >1 mSv per year of life Participation in any prior radiolabelled study within last 5 years History of alcohol abuse or excessive intake of alcohol as judged by the investigator.
